{"TopicId":199847,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Flag Planting Bug","CreatedByName":"Kerbal Productions","CreatedById":208620,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-26T03:51:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal Productions","CreatedById":208620,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-26T03:51:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had been in the Mun several times with 1.11, but I notice: when I plant a flag, it falls then the whole Mun bugs like crazy. The ground, the capsule, nearly everything on the Mun, gone! (well, except for the Kerbal in EVA.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this a bug whatsoever?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-26T04:44:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s known and reported. I\u0027d expect it fixed in 1.11.1 or 1.12.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor now I just plant flags only for contracts, and remove them immediately after.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-29T22:30:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208620-helvica_ring_scientist/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022208620\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208620-helvica_ring_scientist/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Helvica_Ring_Scientist\u003C/a\u003E Looks like it\u0027s fixed in 1.11.1?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223916080\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022199895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221611864000\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167737\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022UomoCapra\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/28/2021 at 3:00 PM, UomoCapra said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Fix placed flags falling down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal Productions","CreatedById":208620,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-30T00:54:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGonna try to check this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dprostock","CreatedById":195079,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-30T20:23:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nErrr....\u00A0I don\u0027t remember, but is there a way to see the badge of a flag planted a long time ago?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}